title: 10/04: Start or Sit (AFC) and "Put Up or Shut Up" Players (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Which players are on the spot this week and could be getting dropped with another bad performance (2:30)? Do we prefer Blake Bortles or Patrick Mahomes this week (7:10)? Are we too low on Derek Carr (10:25)? ... Find out what Jason La Canfora is saying about Le'Veon Bell (12:00) and more news items from around the NFL including OL and defensive injuries that could matter this week ... JAC-KC (23:50), MIA-CIN (34:25), ATL-PIT (39:30), BAL-CLE (42:00), DEN-NYJ (49:21)), TEN-BUF (54:45), OAK-LAC (58:01), DAL-HOU (1:01:58) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
